  "description": "The YISSVIC Electric Fly Swatter delivers instant, mess-free pest control with its powerful 4000V grid, effectively eliminating mosquitoes, flies, and other flying insects. Rechargeable via USB-C (1500mAh battery included), this lightweight zapper features a durable stand base for convenient storage and is ideal for indoor/outdoor use. The pack includes two white rackets for whole-home coverage. Safe, efficient, and odorless—no more chemical sprays or sticky traps!",
